NAME
    Sys::Bprsync - Bullet-proof rsync wrapper

NAME
    Sys::BPrsync - Bullet-proof rsync wrapper

METHODS
  BUILD
    Initialize pre and post exec queues.

  get_cmd_prefix
    Return the command prefix.

  run
    Run the sync.

  vaults
    Return a list of all vaults.

